  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0b95\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd   \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Debate on removal of protestors",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A discussion regarding the removal of the \"Kota Ko Kama\" protestors set up in Galli Mukhathidal area will be held in the Parliament.",
        "Today, Laxman Kiriella, the main organizer of the opposition party, requested the Prime Minister Dines Gunawardena to convene the Parliament for a discussion in this regard.",
        "The government intends to discuss the same issue when Parliament convenes on Wednesday to pass the emergency gazette notification as it is practically difficult to convene Parliament and summon MPs today due to the fuel crisis."
      ],
